SA-ITSI Monitoring and Alerting Content Pack 2.1.0
15 September 2021

This add-on is designed to provide the necessary knowledge objects (dashboards, macros, lookups, etc.) required for the ITSI Content Pack for Monitoring and Alerting (https://docs.splunk.com/Documentation/ITSICP/current/Config/About)

Installation of this Add-On into your Search Head or Search Head Cluster running ITSI is required before the ITSI Content Pack for Monitoring and Alerting can be installed into ITSI using the ITSI restore functionality

For more information about this add-on and the content pack see https://docs.splunk.com/Documentation/ITSICP/current/Config/About
